query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS capabilityCatalog (
  id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  industry VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
  referenceId VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  name VARCHAR(500) NOT NULL,
  description TEXT NOT NULL,
  level INT NOT NULL,
  parentReferenceId VARCHAR(50),
  createdAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  updatedAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  INDEX capability_catalog_industry_idx (industry),
  INDEX capability_catalog_reference_idx (referenceId),
  UNIQUE KEY capability_catalog_unique_ref (industry, referenceId)
)
